---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Whitepaper - ResonantOS" description="The ResonantOS whitepaper page now separates the legacy philosophical foundation from the current DAO-first implementation path.">
	<section class="px-4 pb-16 pt-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
			<p class="mb-5 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-emerald-400">Whitepaper</p>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-6xl">Philosophical foundation, current implementation path.</h1>
			<p class="mt-8 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-8 text-zinc-300">
				The earlier ResonantOS whitepaper explored the Resonant Augmentor, the Oracle and Logician model, and the Symbiotic Shield. That remains part of the philosophical foundation, but the current implementation path is DAO-first.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Legacy Foundation</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-400">
					The concepts of Augmentatism, Resonant Augmentor, executable constitutions, and human-gated evolution still matter. They describe why the work exists.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-lg border border-emerald-400/20 bg-emerald-400/[0.06] p-6">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Current Focus</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-zinc-300">
					The build now starts with official DAO membership credentials, access gates, contribution reputation, and governance mechanics. This is the foundation other ResonantOS contracts can rely on.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">New Whitepaper Outline</h2>
			<ol class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-lg text-zinc-300">
				<li>1. Augmentatism as the philosophical base.</li>
				<li>2. ResonantOS as the shared work and technical system.</li>
				<li>3. ResonantDAO as the governance and membership layer.</li>
				<li>4. Soulbound credentials as originals and access gates.</li>
				<li>5. Human and AI member separation.</li>
				<li>6. Contribution reputation, custodians, and anti-capture governance.</li>
				<li>7. Symbiotic Wallet and AI-agent wallets as later phases.</li>
			</ol>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
